properties.abstract: A breathtaking climb to Alp Sattel and track to Alp Rona, with 360 degrees panoramic views of the Schwnzelegg, followed by a downhill to Sigg.
properties.description: From Grsch the route runs comfortably along the river Landquart. Shortly thereafter the road becomes a narrow single track. But just on the other side of the village Pragg-Jenaz, the climb to Furna awaits the biker. The alpine road then leads to the pass and towards Scra and Schwnzelegg. Once you've reached the top, you are rewarded with a cool downhill towards Sigg. This stretch follows the Schwendi lift. After the hamlet of Sigg the descent runs along the alpine road to Grsch.
